    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>Notitia de terra de Piscina Lifredi et da Sancto Fridiano et de Pratale. In
                        Christi nomine. Breve pro futuris et modernis temporibus securitatem ac
                        firmitatem ad memoriam habendam vel retinendam, qualiter infra civitate
                            <placeName ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/66"
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Mention #Residential #Palatium #Emperor/king"
                            >Pisa</placeName>, in <rs key="#Palatium #Emperor/king">palatio domni
                            regis</rs>, in placido residisse domina <persName key="#Marquis/duke"
                            >Beatrix</persName>
                        <rs key="#Marquis/duke">ducatrix et marchionissa</rs> hac causas audienda
                        hac deliberanda, residentibus cum ea, <persName key="#Judge"
                            >Uberto</persName>, <persName key="#Judge">Winitho</persName>, <persName
                            key="#Judge">Enrigo</persName>, <persName key="#Judge">Ugo</persName>,
                            <persName key="#Judge">Signorecto</persName>, <persName key="#Judge"
                            >Lamberto</persName>, <persName key="#Judge">Ildebrando</persName> et
                        alio <persName key="#Judge">Ugo</persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudicibus</rs>, <persName>Ugo</persName>,
                            <persName>Sesmundo</persName>, <persName>Winizo</persName>,
                            <persName>Bernardo</persName> causidicis, <persName key="#Notary"
                            >Wido</persName>, <persName key="#Notary">Currado</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notariis</rs>, <persName>Sicheri</persName> quondam
                            <persName>Matti</persName>, <persName>Lamberto</persName> quondam
                            <persName>Speciosi</persName>, <persName>Rodilando</persName> quondam
                            <persName>Rollandi</persName>, <persName>Gontulino</persName> quondam
                            <persName>Pandolfi</persName>, <persName>Rodolfino</persName> quondam
                            <persName>Rollandi</persName>, <persName>Erizo</persName> filio
                            <persName>Enrigi</persName>, <persName>Iohanni</persName> quondam
                            <persName>Widi</persName>, <persName>Baroncello</persName> quondam
                            <persName>Hermigarde</persName>, <persName>Glandolfo</persName> quondam
                            <persName>Carli</persName>, <persName>Alcheri</persName> quondam
                            <persName>Ildibrandi</persName>, <persName>Leo</persName> quondam
                            <persName>Rustici</persName>, et reliquis pluribus. Ibique eorum
                        presentiis venientes <persName>Bonitho</persName> prior de <rs
                            key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#http://137.204.128.125/juridical_persons/78"
                            key="#Monasteries">Domini et Sancti Quirici et Sancti Salvatori et
                            Sancte Marie et Sancti Benedicti</orgName> de <placeName
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/86">Populonio</placeName>
                        proclamavit una cum <persName key="#Advocatus">Ugo</persName>
                        <rs key="#Advocatus">avocato</rs> suprascripti monasterii quod
                            <persName>Peregrino</persName> de <placeName
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/132">Vignale</placeName> filius bone
                        menorie *** contendit suprascripto monasterii tres <rs key="#Petiae"
                            >petiis</rs> de terris, quibus sunt positi in loco et finibus <placeName
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/91">Cornino</placeName>, una ubi
                        dicitur <placeName ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/130">Piscina
                            Lifredi</placeName>, secunda ubi dicitur <placeName
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/131">Sancto Fridiano</placeName>,
                        tertia ubi dicitur <placeName ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/131"
                            >Pratale</placeName>, de quibus suprascripto prior una cum <persName
                            key="#Abbots" ref="#http://137.204.128.125/people/108">Cunizo</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbate</rs> suo et de suprascripto monasterio, <rs
                            key="#Judicial_breve">proclamaverunt</rs> domine
                            <persName>Mattilde</persName>. Cum suprascripta domina Beatrix
                        proclamationem audisse, per fustes quas in suis detinebat manibus,
                        investivit cum consilio iudicum suprascripto priore una cum suprascripto
                        avocato suo, pro suprascripto monasterio de suprascriptis tres petiis de
                        terris et insuper misit <rs key="#Emperor/king #Marquis/duke">bannum</rs>
                        domni regis super predicto priore et super iam dicto avocato suo et super
                        predicto monasterio in bisantios aureos duomilia, ut nullus quilibet homo,
                        magna parvaque persona, eodem monasterio de predictis rebus sine legale
                        iudicio disvestire presumat. Qui vero fecerit, predicti duomilia bisanteos
                        aureos composituro se agnoscat, medietatem <rs
                            key="#Emperor/king #Camera_regis">regali camere</rs> et alia
                        medie|[tatem] suprascripti monasterii eiusque rectoribus. Hoc factum est
                        anno dominice incarnationis millesimo septuagesimo VI, idibus martii,
                        indictione quarta Xa. Quidem et ego <persName key="#Notary"
                            >Erimundus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> domni inperatoris ex iussione suprascripte
                        domine Beatrix seo iudicum ammonitjone scripsi. <persName key="#Judge"
                            >Winitho</persName> regis <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs> interfui et
                        subscripsi. <persName key="#Judge">Henricus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs> sacri palatii interfui et subscripsi. <persName
                            key="#Judge">Lambertus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs> sacri palatii interfui et subscripsi. <persName
                            key="#Judge">Ugo</persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs> sacri palatii interfui et subscripsi. <persName
                            key="#Judge">Teodericus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs> sacri palatii interfui et subscripsi.
                            <persName>Ugo</persName> causidicus ibi fui et subscripsi. </ab>
                </div>
